  <governance>
    <issue id="ISS-PKG-TYPE" status="review">
      <statement>The current rqml-core/package.json declares "type": "commonjs", which conflicts with REQ-ESM (publish as an ES module). Decide the final module strategy (ESM-only vs. dual ESM/CJS) and update package.json accordingly.</statement>
    </issue>
    <issue id="ISS-WASM-SOURCE" status="review">
      <statement>Choose the WASM libxml2 distribution (e.g. an existing published build vs. a custom-compiled artifact) and pin its provenance, since REQ-WASM-LIBXML and RISK-WASM-SIZE both depend on this choice.</statement>
    </issue>
  </governance>
</rqml>
